        <updateDate>2020-02-25T22:09:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><STRONG>DD-214 Modernization Act</STRONG></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to modify the Certificate of Release or Discharge from Active Duty (DD Form 214) to include a block in which a member of the Armed Forces may provide an email address by which the member may be contacted after discharge or release from active duty.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
